        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1175">
<l>paṭalāṟṟā paita luḻakkuṅ kaṭalāṟṟāk </l>
<l>kāmanōy ceytaveṉ kaṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Mine eyes have caused me a lust that is greater than the sea and (they themselves) endure the torture of sleeplessness.</l>
